findings.title: Unprotected Sell Fee
findings.description: If sender is not a pair address, sell fee will be taken.

findings.title: Owner can include in and exclude from dividends.
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to include or exclude entities from receiving dividends, which could lead to unfair distribution of funds.

findings.title: Owner Privileges: Fee Inclusion and Exclusion
findings.description: The contract owner has the ability to include or exclude addresses from fee distribution, which can lead to potential manipulation of fees.

findings.title: Owner can change fee receivers
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to modify fee receivers, which could lead to unauthorized changes and potential security risks.

findings.title: Owner can change swap threshold and disable/enable swap.
findings.description: The owner has privileges to modify the swap threshold and enable or disable the swap functionality, which could lead to potential security risks if exploited maliciously.

findings.title: Owner can change distribution criteria.
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to modify the distribution criteria, which could lead to unintended consequences or malicious behavior.

findings.title: Owner can change distribution GAS
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to modify the distribution gas, which could lead to unintended consequences.

findings.title: Owner Can Burn Tokens
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to burn tokens from the contract by sending them to a DEAD address.

findings.title: Owner Privilege: Withdrawal of BNBs
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to withdraw BNBs to the marketing receiver address.
